&lt;p&gt;Set in an ambiance feeling both contemporary and traditional at the same time, Beno&icirc;t Violier stays loyal to tradition with cuisine that has received&lt;strong&gt; 3 Michelin Stars&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;The Elite 100 # 73&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;#88&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants 2013&lt;/strong&gt;. With focus on Swiss ingredients, menus are carefully created. Service is exemplary and the wine list is extensive. Business chic attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the Restaurant de Hotel de Ville Crissier website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://wb.thefork.com/Lausanne-Restaurant_de_l_Hotel_de_Ville_de_Crissier-restaurant/Restaurant_de_l_Hotel_de_Ville_de_Crissier-restaurant-reservation/4a_18062/reservation.html&quot;&gt;http://wb.thefork.com/Lausanne-Restaurant_de_l_Hotel_de_Ville_de_Crissier-restaurant/Restaurant_de_l_Hotel_de_Ville_de_Crissier-restaurant-reservation/4a_18062/reservation.html&lt;/a&gt; or contact Restaurant de Hotel de Ville Crissier by phone at +41 (0)21 634 05 05&nbsp; or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@restaurantcrissier.com&quot;&gt;contact@restaurantcrissier.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide a cell phone number. The restaurant will call you 3 days prior to the dining date to reconfirm and discuss any allergies or special needs. If you don&rsquo;t receive contact from the restaurant by 48 hours prior to the reservation, please contact the restaurant to reconfirm, otherwise the table may be given away&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

